parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unpredictable movement of exterior mirrors can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, and can be a distraction to the driver.
symptoms: Exterior mirrors move on their own
folding forward or backward
and adjusting far outwards
making it difficult to see other vehicles or pedestrians.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The erratic operation of the windshield wipers can reduce visibility during rain or snow, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Windshield wipers operate erratically
moving constantly or not at all
even when set to a specific speed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The lack of individual lighting in the rear compartment can cause glare hazards at night, reducing visibility and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Rear passengers do not have individual lighting
relying on the entire cabin lighting
which can cause glare hazards at night.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake lights can increase the risk of accidents, as other drivers may not be aware of the vehicle's intention to stop, leading to potential rear-end collisions.
symptoms: The brake lights do not illuminate
the brake lights are dim or faint
the brake lights flicker or malfunction
the brake lights stay on continuously
a burning plastic smell is present.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Turn Signal and Hazard Warning Switch Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the turn signal and hazard warning switch can cause the brake lights to malfunction, leading to reduced visibility and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The brake lights do not work
the brake lights stay on continuously
the turn signals do not work
the hazard warning lights do not work
a burning plastic smell is present.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the high beam headlights can reduce visibility while driving at night, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The high beam headlights throw a beam of light almost straight up
reducing visibility while driving on dark roads at night.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sun gear in the transmission can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to loss of power, stalling, or difficulty shifting gears, which can increase the risk of accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates when shifting gears
the vehicle shudders or bucks
the vehicle surges or hesitates when accelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended engagement of 4-wheel drive can cause loss of control, accidents, or difficulty steering, which can increase the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The 4-wheel drive system engages without warning
the vehicle pulls to one side
the vehicle is difficult to steer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping and hesitation can cause loss of power, stalling, or difficulty shifting gears, which can increase the risk of accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates when shifting gears
the vehicle shudders or bucks
the vehicle surges or hesitates when accelerating
the ignition switch fails.
